reviewText: I experienced the magic from Fantasy in Lights 5 or more years ago and it was amazing, I loved it and couldn't wait to tell everyone and to share it with my friends and family. My husband and I went yesterday... WHAT HAPPENED? you downsized, theres no way you have as many lights as you advertise, it is nothing like the commercials or ads show/advertise anymore, it used to be. It was a 2 hour drive for us and we were so shocked and disappointed. Plus it was expensive just for something we could have seen locally...
